snippet.title: The Cookbook Method of Learning Programming Languages
snippet.description:
Learn new programming languages and explore interesting topics using the Cookbook Method. NanoDano@DevDungeon.com explains his recommended path to learning new programming languages.

Check out the DevDungeon Cookbook for inspiration.

http://www.devdungeon.com/cookbook

https://github.com/DevDungeon/Cookbook
